room_title: Escape room "Jack the Ripper" by Escape Room Palm Springs in Palm Springs
room_address: 2500 N. Palm Canyon Dr., #B3, Palm Springs, CA 92262
room_description: Transport yourself to the slums of Victorian London where you’ll help Scotland Yard solve the Jack the Ripper murders, hopefully without ending up as the next victim. You and your team will uncover evidence that will help you identify the killer as you work through the game. But if you think identifying the world’s most notorious serial killer will be simple, then you don’t know Jack.
